templates, you can create a Cocoa-based action

00:43:13.409 --> 00:43:16.730
if you want to write your run code in Objective-C.

00:43:16.730 --> 00:43:22.110
If you want to write your run code in shell you can use
the shell template and create an Automator action that's

00:43:22.110 --> 00:43:25.360
in shell or you can use the new
the Cocoa AppleScript template

00:43:25.360 --> 00:43:31.320
and create yourself an AppleScript-based
Automator action as well.

